item.title: About
item.description: Hi. I’m Zad. That’s me above. This is a blog where I discuss scientific studies in depth. A lot of the blog will focus on biostatistics, research methods, evidence, and data science (mainly with R & Stata) so if you haven’t run away yet, welcome.
